703622f-b.title: Brooklyn: Classon Avenue - Prospect Place
703622f-b.text:
Classon Avenue, east side, north from ~rospect Place, showing the
Jewish Hospital. View 2 shows thw Prospect Place side of the
hespital.
View 3 is at the southeast corner of Cbasson and Prospect, show-
ing the Brooklyn Home for Aged Men.
P. L. -perr  September 14, 1941
NO REPPODUCTIONS  Views 1-3
